Package syntax

Class FunctionalSymbolTerm

java.lang.Object
syntax.Term
syntax.FunctionalSymbolTerm
public final class FunctionalSymbolTerm extends Term
A representation of a term consisting of a functional symbol of non-zero arity and a list of child terms.
